**Under-construction properties** require payment in stages (10–20% on booking, then construction-linked milestones). During construction, you pay 'pre-EMI' — interest only on the amount disbursed, not full EMI. However, this pre-EMI is not deductible as interest on home loan until possession. GST at 5% (or 1% for affordable housing) also applies on under-construction properties.
